data.description: Country living at its finest! With a beautiful view and just over 5 acres, this lovely 2 BD, 1 1/2 bath home is the perfect place to call Home Sweet Home!  In the winter months you can cozy up next to the fireplace and watch the snow fall and, in the summer, enjoy sun filled days at one of the PNW most beautiful lakes just a few minutes away. 17 mins to I-5 access.
